LibBi README file
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The LibBi package (nominally "Library for Bayesian inference", pronounced
"Libby").


Installation
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

See the INSTALL file.


Documentation
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Documentation of all Perl modules is available via perldoc, e.g.:

perldoc lib/Bi/Model.pm

The user manual may be built, from the base directory of LibBi, using the
command:

perl MakeDocs.PL

The manual may then be accessed at docs/pdf/index.pdf.

Source code documentation may be built using doxygen with the following
command:

doxygen

HTML documentation can then be accessed at docs/dev/html/index.html.
